snippet.title: Hot Wheels™: Race Off+ Available Now on Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Buckle up! Hot Wheels: Race Off+ is available now on Apple Arcade!


Hot Wheels: Race Off+ brings the ultimate adrenaline-fueled racing experience to your fingertips. Collect and upgrade iconic Hot Wheels cars and speed across insane tracks filled with gravity-defying loops, epic jumps, and heart-pounding stunts.


Play now: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hot-wheels-race-off/id6670202361
